line.en: Without thinking, I bluntly reply and Amane seems\na little hurt.
'Ah... Well I don't 'like' you in that way, I\nmean!'
'I like being around you, and I like you in that\nsense!'
As I hastily try to clarify things, Amane looks\nlike she's relieved.
'Me too. I like you, Aoi, and everyone else too.'
